ZH: 我是一个忠实的朋友。
EN: I am a loyal friend.

ZH: 她对工作非常忠实。
EN: She is very loyal to her job.

ZH: 宠物狗对主人非常忠实。
EN: Pet dogs are very loyal to their owners.

ZH: 我爸爸是一位忠实的军人。
EN: My father is a loyal soldier.

ZH: 她是一个忠实的支持者，总是支持我。
EN: She is a loyal supporter, always supporting me.

ZH: 忠实的读者会记住好书的作者。
EN: Loyal readers will remember the authors of good books.

ZH: 他对家乡忠实不移。
EN: He is loyal to his hometown.

ZH: 我对我的祖国忠实。
EN: I am loyal to my motherland.

ZH: 忠实的员工会全心全意为公司工作。
EN: Loyal employees will work wholeheartedly for the company.

ZH: 她对自己的职责忠实不二。
EN: She is loyal to her own responsibilities.

ZH: 要成为一个忠实的朋友，需要互相信任。
EN: To become a loyal friend, trust is needed.

ZH: 他对他的承诺忠实不渝。
EN: He is faithful to his promises.

ZH: 忠实的球迷会一直支持他们喜欢的团队。
EN: Loyal fans will always support the teams they like.

ZH: 忠实的伴侣会在对方最困难的时候支持他们。
EN: Loyal partners will support each other in their toughest times.

ZH: 她对她的家人忠实无比。
EN: She is incredibly loyal to her family.

ZH: 忠实的艺术追随者会欣赏各种不同的艺术形式。
EN: Loyal art followers will appreciate various forms of art.

ZH: 这个品牌的忠实顾客会一直选择他们的产品。
EN: Loyal customers of this brand will always choose their products.

ZH: 作为一个忠实的员工，他总是按时完成任务。
EN: As a loyal employee, he always completes tasks on time.

ZH: 忠实的信徒会不断追随他们的宗教教义。
EN: Faithful believers will continuously follow their religious doctrines.

ZH: 他是这个组织最忠实的成员之一。
EN: He is one of the most loyal members of this organization.
